sequenceDiagram
    participant R1 as Request A (list)
    participant R2 as Request B (list)
    participant R3 as Request C (spawn)
    participant RW as RwLock HashMap
    participant MAP as HashMap data

    Note over RW: Estado inicial — livre

    R1->>RW: read().await
    RW->>MAP: guarda leitura (shared)
    Note over RW: 1 leitor ativo

    R2->>RW: read().await
    RW->>MAP: guarda leitura (shared)
    Note over RW: 2 leitores simultâneos OK

    R1->>MAP: values() → AgentRecords
    R2->>MAP: values() → AgentRecords
    R1-->>RW: drop guard (read)
    R2-->>RW: drop guard (read)
    Note over RW: livre de novo

    R3->>RW: write().await
    Note over R3,RW: exclusivo — ninguém mais entra
    RW->>MAP: insert(agent_id, entry)
    R3-->>RW: drop guard (write)
    Note over RW: livre

    Note over R1,R3: Regra: vários read OU um write, nunca os dois juntos
